    <h1>My Study Snippets</h1>
    <h3>A useful application to create, read, and update Snippets of
        technical subjects you want to master.
    </h3>
    <% if logged_in? %>
         <a href="/snippets/<%=current_user.id%>" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">View All Your Snippets</a>
         <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Logout</a>
